"""Check if write function called"""
mock_append_wdc_data.return_value = self.wdc_data
io.wdc_to_hourly_csv(wdc_path=self.wdc_path, write_dir=self.write_dir,
    obs_list=self.obs_list, print_obs=self.print_obs)
mock_write_csv_data.assert_called_with(data=self.wdc_data, write_dir=self.
    write_dir, obs_name=self.obs_list[0])
mock.patch('magpysv.io.write_csv_data')mock.patch('magpysv.io.append_wdc_data')mock.patch('os.path.exists', return_value=True)
